water-blade-runner-three-billboards-full-list-1202239064/|title=\u2018The Shape Of Water\u2019 Leads BAFTA Film Awards Nominations \u2013 Full List|last=Tartaglione|first=Nancy|publisher=[[Deadline Hollywood]]|date=9 January 2018|accessdate=9 January 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| North Texas Film Critics Association\n| Best Animated Film\n| rowspan=\"2\"| Dorota Kobiela and Hugh Welchman\n| {{draw|2nd Place}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.northtexasfilmcritics.com/home/the-best-of-2017-from-the-ntfca|title=Best of 2017 from the NTFCA|last=Tapley|first=Kristopher|date=23 December 2017|work=North Texas Film Critics Association|accessdate=23 December 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[St. Louis Film Critics Association]]\n| [[St. Louis Gateway Film Critics Association Award for Best Animated Film|Best Animated Feature]]\n| {{Nominated}}\n|<ref name=\"Amidi\"/>\n|-\n| Phoenix Film Critics Society Awards\n| Best Animated Film\n| rowspan=\"4\"|''Loving Vincent''\n| {{nom}}\n|<ref>{{cite web|last=Amidi|first=Amid|title=Phoenix Film Critics Society|url=https://www.phoenixfilmcriticssociety.org/2017-nominees.html|accessdate=14 December 2017|publisher=2017 Awards NOMINATIONS|date=14 December 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171213143403/https://www.phoenixfilmcriticssociety.org/2017-nominees.html|archive-date=13 December 2017|url-status=dead|df=dmy-all}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Alliance of Women Film Journalists]]\n| Best Animated Film\n| {{won}}\n| <ref>{{cite web|url=http://awfj.org/eda-awards-2/2017-awfj-eda-award-nominees/|title=2017 AWFJ EDA Award Nominees|publisher=[[Alliance of Women Film Journalists]]|date=3 January 2018|accessdate=3 January 2018|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20180103084642/http://awfj.org/eda-awards-2/2017-awfj-eda-award-nominees/|archivedate=3 January 2018|url-status=live}}</ref>\n|-\n|Denver Film Critics Society Awards\n| Best Animated Film\n| {{nom}}\n|<ref>{{cite web| title=\u2018Call Me By Your Name\u2019 Leads Denver Film Critics Society (DFCS) Nominations