]]'' \u2013 Casey Kessler\n* ''[[Red Dead Redemption 2]]'' \u2013 Vernon Cherry, Jack\n* ''[[Skyrim]]: Falskaar'' \u2013 Kalevi\n* ''[[Street Fighter V]]'' \u2013 Xiayu\n* ''[[The Nameless Mod]]'' \u2013 Hao Niu-rou-->\n<!-- NEED NOTABILITY\n|2007\n|''Gladiator Trials II''\n|Peasants, Gladiators\n|\n| (resume 2)\n|-\n|2008\n|''The Tales of Bingwood''\n|Tombrandt Driftwood, Kitchen Boy\n|\n| (resume 2)\n|-\n|2009\n|''7.62: High Calibre''\n|Collin Woods, Sylvester McNabb, Tomi Mengazi\n|\n| (resume 2)\n|-\n|2009\n|''7.62''\n|Collin Woods, Sylvester McNabb, Tomi Mengazi\n|\n| (resume 2)\n|-\n|2009\n|''Elven Legacy''\n|Player\n|\n| (resume 2)\n|-\n|2013\n|''Seven-G F/A-18 Flight Simulator''\n|Pilot, Tower Control\n|\n| (resume 2)\n|-\n|2013\n|''Whispers: Revelation''\n|Lost Little Boy\n|\n| (resume 2)\n|-\n|2014\n|''Ghost Encounters: Deadwood''\n|Billy\n|\n| (resume 2)\n|-\n|2015\n|''Dungeons: The Eye of Draconus''\n|Rohan, Smurvs, Papa Smurv, Various\n|\n| (resume 2)\n|-\n|2016\n|''Backstage Pass''\n|Benito\n|\n| (resume 2)\n|-\n|2016\n|''Mystery of the Ancients: Mud Water Creek''\n|Arlene\n|\n| (resume 2)\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''Food Fantasy''\n|Long Bao, Omurice, Salad, Spicy Hot Pot\n|\n| Tweet<ref>{{cite web |last=Mongillo |first=Casey |title=Food Fantasy: Long Bao, Salad, Omurice, and Spicy Hot Pot |url=https://twitter.com/caseytheva/status/1020398979186475008?lang=en |website=Twitter |accessdate=October 20, 2019 |language=en |date=July 20, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n|2019\n|''Intruders: Hide and Seek''\n|Ben Richter\n|\n| Tweet<ref>{{cite web |last=Mongillo |first=Casey |title=Intruders: Ben |url=https://twitter.com/CaseyTheVA/status/1110327473437200384 |website=Twitter |accessdate=October 20, 2019 |language=en |date=March 25, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n|2019\n|''KurtzPel''\n|Male Player\n| Shy & Healer characters\n| Instagram<ref>{{cite web |last=Mongillo |first=Casey |title=KurtzPel: Male Player (Shy & Healer) |url=https://www.instagram.com/p/BxAyaCzleuA/ |website=Instagram |accessdate